{"tid":1242812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共有可能放棄獨裁和一黨專政嗎？  看似不可能，但不要排除這個可能性。","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:03:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bab6d470aca3f28c560fdeb526cb5482105c65","tid":1242812,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"中共有可能放棄獨裁和一黨專政嗎？<br />\n<br />\n看似不可能，但不要排除這個可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在特朗普的不斷追擊下，中共國已經奄奄一息，昨晚深夜，特朗普發Twitter說，習帝願意在G20見面。<br />\n<br />\n早前，特朗普說，如果習帝不願來G20見面，就會加徵3250億美元中國貨25%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n習帝受到如此巨大侮辱，還要乖乖見特朗普，表明他已經走投無路了，中共國只有兩條路可走：<br />\n<br />\n選擇蘇共模式自我解體，抑或選擇羅馬尼亞模式被推翻解體？"},{"pid":"eb75d85473960cffb962b10a88aa47ce847539e0","tid":1242812,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/777960282599813?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FLamCheng%2Fpermalink%2F777960282599813%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8da7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=209ef307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/LamCheng/permalink/777960282599813?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"969b53666d872065ed3d25ec638604142d9c6831","tid":1242812,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}